{"tid":456081,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[篤得太誇] 啟德次等主場館成本貴過歐洲最豪溫布萊球場","createTime":"2017-11-02T15:58:41.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-03T08:52:07.000Z","uid":82640,"like":64,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":37,"replies":[{"pid":"cf8266993dc521bcc9afde2c1250d857a9eb1a10","tid":456081,"uid":82640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T15:58:41.000Z","msg":"有睇開英超都知熱剌因為主場重修而搬咗去溫布萊球場<br />\n熱剌個新主場6萬1千個位起喺嘅倫敦起都只係40億港紙<br />\n仲要包埋拆咗舊場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n睇返香港啟德體育城個主場館50000個位都冇要88億港紙<br />\n洲際比賽決賽都唔合規格嘅場點解成本要一倍再加一<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n再睇清楚啲<br />\n條數未包括買入面啲設備、整平塊地、打樁之類<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n只係計返主場館成本加埋已經120億+<br />\n<br />\n歐洲最豪華球場倫敦溫布萊球場<br />\n成本全歐最貴都只係107億（已經計算2017年通漲）<br />\n但100億已經包括個商場、停車場、博物館etc...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n踢波裝到87,000係啟德主場館一倍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n政府份文件字裡行間講參考外國例子<br />\n貴成咁真係唔知搵邊個做reference<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n熱剌主場成本source：<a href=\"http://www.goal.com/hk/news/491/英格蘭/2017/01/05/31149082/熱刺新球場興建如火如荼\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.goal.com%2Fhk%2Fnews%2F491%2F%E8%8B%B1%E6%A0%BC%E8%98%AD%2F2017%2F01%2F05%2F31149082%2F%E7%86%B1%E5%88%BA%E6%96%B0%E7%90%83%E5%A0%B4%E8%88%88%E5%BB%BA%E5%A6%82%E7%81%AB%E5%A6%82%E8%8D%BC&d=syQBijTYAEaLgee73pzTvf1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=17231878\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.goal.com/hk/news/491/英格蘭/2017/01/05/31149082/熱刺新球場興建如火如荼</a><br />\n<br />\n啟德成本source：<a href=\"http://www.legco.gov.hk/yr16-17/chinese/fc/pwsc/papers/p17-02c.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.legco.gov.hk%2Fyr16-17%2Fchinese%2Ffc%2Fpwsc%2Fpapers%2Fp17-02c.pdf&d=syQBijTYAEaLgee73pzTvf1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=270c9931\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.legco.gov.hk/yr16-17/chinese/fc/pwsc/papers/p17-02c.pdf</a><br />\n<br />\n溫布萊球場成本source：wiki都有"},{"pid":"c642d1b54b0f831642364eafe01b3b04c0a76d64","tid":456081,"uid":60648,"like":1,"dislike":22,"score":-21,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T15:59:59.000Z","msg":"香港人人工貴，仲貴過d死鬼佬<br />\n<br />\n好似係"},{"pid":"62ffea7d02baec71687559d6d4ccbe0bfa62ca3f","tid":456081,"uid":14719,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T16:01:27.000Z","msg":"熱刺起緊個新場好似有得自動換草皮 一個踢波用 一個欖球用<br />\n香港依家個個用咁多錢 我覺起碼要有熱刺個個質素"},{"pid":"ea2412a654cbea39d6a2f21fa83e984bad71c0b9","tid":456081,"uid":61280,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T16:01:52.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">你未計港共慣例，超支追加預算喎，預多50%冇走雞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ！！！！</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"5ead3c1765b8c10d76d5bf441f12d129244a3212","tid":456081,"uid":19552,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T16:02:52.000Z","msg":"熱狗主場贏埋皇馬 香港果個場贏咩先"},{"pid":"2493c2a9fe6fac9548a4b98ce237cf0341403281","tid":456081,"uid":36238,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T16:03:18.000Z","msg":"香港判頭食水深"},{"pid":"1dd47a40680049262dc98987d1d7cef150864a13","tid":456081,"uid":105995,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T16:05:06.000Z","msg":"利益輸送支那公司<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8da8bb1f4fbbec4ae3daef18960e74d0c3546fd8","tid":456081,"uid":23993,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T16:11:51.000Z","msg":"貴？<br />\n條數盡量寫細架啦 方便之後同政府再攞架啦喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6259ef96bce8baad92d16adb121bf3acc8f4df69","tid":456081,"uid":18251,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"ci